      <div class="msgContentFrame">New keyboard mappings are very promising &amp; useful, though very standard in the genre as well.   <br /> <br />Increase to the mob population may help to make some of the vast landscapes seem less barren.  <br /> <br />And more room is always an improvement; I filled up my bag and my retainer in my second day of playing.  Mostly because I can only sell so few items at a time. </div>
