umber of spawns. <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 19th 2010  3:44pm by Zorvan </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1815523.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
